      • index

        private int index
        Initialized value at 0. At any time it indicates what is the index of the next node to initiate. When it comes to size, we know that we have initiated a sufficient number of nodes to start the algorithm.

      • ready

        private int ready
        Initialized value at 0 At any time it indicates how many nodes Have finished their initialization procedures. We expect all actors to receive the message of creation before they start, otherwise they receive messages from other actors already ready, but they put them in unprepared structures
